HEADWORD: Uncompromising
<hw>Un*com"pro*mi`sing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not
admitting of compromise; making no truce or concessions; obstinate;
unyielding; inflexible.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Un*com"pro*mi`sing*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unconceivable</ent>⟦br⟧
